videos.headline: Arizona State scores first TD
videos.description: Manny Wilkins finds Kyle Williams down the middle of the field for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Richard's TD gives Sun Devils big lead
videos.description: Demario Richard sees a gap in the defense and bursts through for a 17-yard touchdown, giving Arizona State a 23-0 lead.

videos.headline: Richard's 2nd TD gives Sun Devils early blowout
videos.description: Demario Richard takes the hand-off and runs it in for an easy 1-yard touchdown giving Arizona State a 30-0 lead.

videos.headline: Oregon State showing some fight with Nall rushing TD
videos.description: Ryan Nall cuts back to his right and scores a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Richard scores 3rd TD for the Sun Devils
videos.description: Demario Richard runs through a defender and scores a 3-yard touchdown.
